# Réception
Local File PRECEIPT [PTH], PRECEIPT [PTH2]
Filter [PTH2] Order By Key CLE=CREDAT
For [PTH2]
 ISITE = find([F:PTH2]PRHFCY,GSITE(1..GNBSITE))
