  Gosub TRA3
  If GOK<1 : Break : Endif
 Endif
Next
Close Local File [PTH], [PTH2]
If GOK<1 Return Endif

# Demande d'achat détail
Local File PREQUISD [PSD], PREQUISD [PSD2]
Filter [PSD2] Order By Key CLE=CREDAT
For [PSD2]
 ISITE = find([F:PSD2]PRHFCY,GSITE(1..GNBSITE))
 If ISITE & GSOCSITE(ISITE)=[F:CPY2]CPY
  Call DEBTRANS From GLOCK
  Gosub TRA4
  If GOK<1 : Break : Endif
 Endif
Next
Close Local File [PSD], [PSD2]
If GOK<1 Return Endif

# Réception temporaire
Local File PWRKPTH [PWH], PWRKPTH [PWH2]
Filter [PWH2] Order By Key CLE=CREDAT
For [PWH2]
 ISITE = find([F:PWH2]PRHFCY,GSITE(1..GNBSITE))
